  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EventArrayAdapter.OnEventListener
    Listens for event and calls onEventClick with given position when event occurs.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Constants
    Constants used to control which vesion of the API is called
    Error
    Error class containing information about errors that occur
    Event
    Event that contains the information returned from the API and needed to display on the UI

    EventDetailsActivity

    OkHttpHandler

    Registrant

    RegistrantArrayAdapter

    RegistrantArrayAdapter.ViewHolder

    RegistrantInfoActivity
    RegistrantInfoActivity is the activity which controllers the view when used for viewing registrants of an event
    SuccessDialog

    UserEvent
